{"tid":2516172,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"外國媒體: 損害香港的新聞自由將會損害香港經濟","createTime":"2021-05-04T13:00:06.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T13:06:57.000Z","uid":94771,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"196a875f1585f3417668b2196744a1a87c672f69","tid":2516172,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T13:00:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/ForeignPolicy/status/1389354082515701761?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FForeignPolicy%2Fstatus%2F1389354082515701761%3Fs%3D20&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=28918fec\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FForeignPolicy%2Fstatus%2F1389354082515701761%3Fs%3D20&h=a669b607\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/ForeignPolicy/status/1389354082515701761?s=20</a><br />\n<br />\nRTHK玩壞埋，假新聞法又話要立，又會＂完善＂媒體制度<br />\n所以一個所謂&quot;國際金融中心&quot; <br />\n係唔係可以係一個<ins>新聞資訊自由受限制</ins>的地方繼續<span class=\"gold\"><strong>行穩致遠</strong></span>，<span class=\"gold\"><strong>再出發</strong></span>就幾值得討論<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"orange\"><p class=\"center\"><span class=\"x-large\">國際文宣好需要大家 - <br />\n每POST更新<ins>4/5</ins><br />\n<br />\n力量及效果可能微不足道，但積小成多可能有意想不到的效果出現</span></p></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>點解仲有Twitter，Reddit戰線？因為香港人仲未有第二個平台連繫全世界，<span class=\"orange\">最重要係全球支持香港的政要，組織仲係Twitter為主要活躍</span>，短時間難以找到取代</ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"orange\"><strong><span class=\"teal\">Twitter</span>本日推薦 每日更新</strong></span></span><br />\nRTHK刪片<br />\n<blockquote><a href=\"https://twitter.com/RSF_en/status/1389551837741654020?s=20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRSF_en%2Fstatus%2F1389551837741654020%3Fs%3D20&d=qHuNkoJYq05zO%2BFPSordK4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=8fe1a5b0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRSF_en%2Fstatus%2F1389551837741654020%3Fs%3D2